{"word":"κερδίων","slug":"κερδίων","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n56837\" key=\"kerdi/wn\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"suff\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">κερδ-ίων</orth>, <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ον</itype>, gen. <itype lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"itype\">ονος</itype>, <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"comp\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Comp.\">Comp.</a></gram> </gramGrp> (with no Posit. in use), formed from <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κέρδος</foreign>, <sense id=\"n56837.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">more profitable</tr_>; <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Hom.</author> </bibl> only neut., <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἐμοὶ δέ κε κέρδιον εἴη</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:6:410\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">6.410</biblScope></bibl></cit>, or <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">καί κεν πολὺ κέρδιον ἦεν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:41\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.41</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:7:28\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">7.28</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἦ μάλα τοι τόδε κ. ἔπλετο θυμῷ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:20:304\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">20.304</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>: later in masc., <cit TEIform=\"c